/* Classes
   Employee: Base class with name and userId as members.
   HR_Employee: Inherits from Employee and includes methods
   for viewing, and searching employees.
   Manager: Inhereits from Employee and provides a method to
   view the employee's own information.
   General Employee: Inherits from Employee and provides a method
   to view the employee's own information. */

/* Functions
   login(): Handles user authentication and creates the 
   appropriate Employee object based on credentials.
   hrMenu(): Desplays the HR menu and handles user input for 
   HR-specific operations.
   managerMenu(): Displays the Management menu and handles user input. */
